                <mxCell id="3" value="&lt;font style=&quot;color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;Open Authentication: - OAuth is a way to let one app access another app’s data &lt;strong data-end=&quot;89&quot; data-start=&quot;56&quot;&gt;without sharing our password&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/font&gt;" style="text;strokeColor=default;fillColor=none;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;spacingLeft=4;spacingRight=4;overflow=hidden;points=[[0,0.5],[1,0.5]];portConstraint=eastwest;rotatable=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;dashed=1;dashPattern=1 4;" vertex="1" parent="2">
